{"tid":1449531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］我地今日又撚狗大勝","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:09:34.000Z","uid":218699,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"65bd50bb06e420060e69d8cf0e389260fcef591e","tid":1449531,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你啦 以後唔好再有人同我話乜嘢贏咗 乜撚嘢贏咗民意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地要記住.....<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地一直都輸緊5比0</span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求一個都未回應<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5條人命 數百手足被捕 無數鮮血<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n但得到係乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔好再宣傳乜嘢贏緊呀 呢啲只係短暫勝利</span><br />\n<br />\n我地腳下已經有唔少屍體踩住啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係仲想同我呀Q精神吖？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唯有一直抗爭落去 直到勝利 先對得住犧性咗嘅手足烈士</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRqQq74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRqQq74.jpg&h=1cf42338&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e6873479cffca0dc8dbf5edade96990698d67f3","tid":1449531,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31a1d399ceffb55410e88e08f110a829be87436","tid":1449531,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5064c0b7481d4c2cde17f854e62f726a40ab5bb0","tid":1449531,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.